\id AMO
\h Ɛamus 
\toc1 Ɛamus 
\toc2 Ɛamus 
\toc3 Ɛam. 
\mt1 Ɛamus  
\c 1
\s1 Řeḥkamat Yahuda d Israil u x timmura i d asent-i-dd innḍen  
\m
\v 1 Awařen n Ɛamus, wenni tuɣa iǧan jar imeksawen n Taquɛa, \add awařen\add* i iẓra x Israil, deg wussan n Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d Yarubɛam, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, tnayen n iseggʷusa qbeř i wenhezzi n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Zak. 14:5\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 2 Netta inna: “SIDI ad izehhar zi Ṣihyun, ad issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes zi Urcalim. Ddmani n tarewsa ad ceḍnent u taqiccet n Karmil ad tisřaw.” \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Irm. 25:30; Yuw. 4:16\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Dimacq\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni ssarwaten Jilɛad s teřwiḥin itteḥřuǧuḍen n wuzzař i usarwet.  
\v 4 Ad ssekkeɣ timessi di taddart n Ḥazayil, ad tecc řeqṣur n Binhadad.  
\v 5 Ad arẓeɣ zzekrun n Dimacq u ad mḥiɣ wenni izeddɣen zi Buqɛa-Awan, \add zi řewḍa n wareddeǧ\add*, d wenni zi taddart n meẓri i yarebbun azeǧaḍ, u řgens n Aram ad ittwandeh di tmeḥbast ɣar Qir!, inna SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt 2 Ij. 16:9; Ica. 17:1-11; Irm. 49:23-27\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Ɣazza\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni iwyen \add řgens inu\add* qaɛ di lmenfa, ḥima ad \add t\add* sellmen i Idum. \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Im. 21:16, 17; 28:18\x*  
\v 7 Ad ssekkeɣ timessi daxeř di řeḥyuḍ n Ɣazza, ad tecc řeqṣur nnes.  
\v 8 Necc ad teḥḥiɣ amezduɣ zi Acdud u zi Acqalun wenni yarebbun azeǧaḍ u Necc ad ksiɣ afus inu ḍidd i Ɛaqrun u min iqqimen n ayt n Ifilisṭiniyyen ad ittwahellek, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Ṣur\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni sellmen \add řgens inu\add* qaɛ di lmenfa i Idum, war idaren řɛahd ak-d wawmaten nsen.  
\v 10 S uyenni ad ssekkeɣ timessi daxeř di řeḥyuḍ n Ṣur, ad tecc řeqṣur nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Idum\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi netta iḍfar awmaten nnes s ssif u issɛiǧi arreḥmet nnes, u \add minzi\add* aɣḍab nnes iqqim icarreg břa qeṭṭu, u \add minzi\add* aheddi n uduqqez nnes \add n ufugem\add* iqqim \add issaggwad\add* řebda.  
\v 12 Necc ad ssekkeɣ timessi di Tayman, ad tecc řeqṣur n Buṣra.”   
\b  
\m
\v 13 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i iggin\add* \bd ayt n Ɛammun\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni carrgen timɣarin s ddeyset zi Jilɛad, ḥima ad sswessɛen tammurt nsen.  
\v 14 Necc ad ssarɣeɣ ict n tmessi daxeř i řeḥyuḍ n Rabba, ad tecc řeqṣur nnes, ɣar iɣuyyan deg wass n umenɣi, am isuḍ usemmiḍ deg wass n tḥaryaḍt.  
\v 15 Ajeǧid nsen ad yuyur di lmenfa, netta ak-d řḥukkam nnes, inna SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\m
\v 1 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Mu’ab\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni sscemḍen iysan n ujeǧid n Idum ařami dewřen d jjir.  
\v 2 Necc ad ssekkeɣ timessi di Mu’ab, ad tecc řeqṣur n Qaryut. Mu’ab ad immet ɣar ddriz ameqqran, ɣar iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add* \add u\add* ɣar řḥess n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri.  
\v 3 Necc ad teḥḥiɣ řqaḍi zi řwest nnes u ad nɣeɣ marra řḥukkam nnes akides, iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Yahuda\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni war qbiřen Ccariɛa n SIDI u war ṭṭifen di tweṣṣa inu u \add minzi\add* \add irebbiten nsen\add* n ixarriqen, inni ḍfaren řejdud nsen, arrin ten weddaren,  
\v 5 Necc ad ssekkeɣ timessi di Yahuda, ad tecc řeqṣur n Urcalim.”   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Ammu i inna SIDI: X třata n ixeṭṭan \add i igga\add* \bd Isra’il\bd*, \add ɛad mahu\add* x arebɛa, war t ssbeṭṭařeɣ, minzi nitni zzenzen amsegged s \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart u amezřuḍ i tyuya n sandaliyat.  
\v 7 Nitni tecḍiḍiḥen ɣar tɛejjajt x uzeǧif n imuqřiřen u nitni ttbellaɛen abrid n imwaḍɛen \add břa ssibbet\add*. Aryaz d babas ruḥen ɣar teḥramt d ict, ḥima ad feḍḥen Isem inu iqeddsen.  
\v 8 Nitni sswaẓẓaḍen ixef nsen zzat mkuř aɛalṭar x warruḍ i dd-ittwarehnen u di taddart n arebbi nsen sessen binu \add ssaɣen t s tmenyat\add* n yinni x ittwagg multa.  
\v 9 D Necc i tuɣa \add din\add* teḥḥiɣ Imuriyyen zzat i uɣembub nsen, inni tuɣa yuɛřan am tneglin yuɛřan u jehhden am tcejjura n řbeǧuḍ. Necc teḥḥiɣ řɣiǧet nnes sennej u iẓewran nnes swadday. \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt Řxř. 21:24; Aɛwd. 2:31; Yac. 24:8\x*  
\v 10 D Necc i tuɣa kenniw i dd-issgeɛɛden zi Miṣra u arriɣ kenniw tuyurem arebɛin n iseggʷusa di řexřa, maḥend ad tᵉṭṭfem tammurt n Imuriyyen d řwart. \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Uf. 12:51\x*  
\v 11 Zeg iḥenjiren nwem arriɣ zzaysen inabiyyen u zeg iḥudriyyen nwem \add arriɣ zzaysen\add* inni tuɣa yarebbun ttaj \add n ucuwwaf n lwaɛd\add*. Ma war iǧi amenni, \add a\add* ayt n Israil?!, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 12 Kenniw \add maca\add* tarrim inni tuɣa yarebbun ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* ad swen binu u kenniw tweṣṣam inabiyyen, tennam: ‘Kenniw war ɣarwem bu ttesriḥ, ḥima ad tnebbam!’ \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Ɛam. 7:12, 13\x*  
\v 13 Xzar, Necc ad awem ɛebbzeɣ swadday am yict n tkarrut teccur s tqebbiḍin \add n imendi\add* tɛebbez \add tijarrarin nnes di temmurt swadday\add*.  
\v 14 Aqa ṣafi tarewřa i wenni ifsusen, u wenni ijehden war izemmar ad iḥḍa jjehd nnes u bu-teɣřuḍt war izemmar ad issenjem tudart nnes.  
\v 15 Wenni iṭṭfen di řqews, war \add ittɣimi\add* ibedd, u wenni izemmaren x tazřa, war inejjem, u wenni ineddhen ayis, war izemmar ad issenjem řeɛmar nnes.  
\v 16 Wenni izeɛɛmen qaɛ jar ayt n bu-teɣruḍt ad yarweř d aɛaryan \bd deg wass nni\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Řḥukm n SIDI x Israil d Samarya  
\m
\v 1 “Sřem awař-a i kidwem issawař SIDI, \add a\add* ayt n Israil, ak-d kuř řaǧ nni ssgeɛɛdeɣ Necc zi temmurt n Miṣra, am qqareɣ:  
\v 2 ‘Zi marra řaǧat n ddunect ssneɣ mɣir kenniw. X uya ad kenniw ɛaqbeɣ x marra řmuɛṣiyyat nwem!  
\v 3 Ma ad uyuren tnayen ak-d wayawya, břa ma ttafqen?  
\v 4 Ma ad izehhar wayrad deg wezɣar řami war ɣares bu zzardet? Ma ayrad d ameẓyan ad yejj tmijja nnes ad tᵉttwaseř zeg yefri, am war imniɛ walu? \f ◼ \fr 3:4 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 5 Ma ad inḍar wejḍiḍ di řfex x \add wudem n\add* temmurt, mařa war din \add dayes\add* macca i netta? Ma ad innurfeɛ řfex zi temmurt mařa texwa?  
\v 6 Mařa \add ḥed\add* isuḍ deg uyicc n icarri di tendint, ma war ittarjiji řgens? Mařa imsar ijj n uceřwaw di tendint, ma war tt iggi SIDI?\x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Ica. 45:7; Igjd. 3:37, 38\x*  
\v 7 Maɣar Sidi inu, SIDI, war ittegg uřa d ict n řḥajet břa ma ad issargeb ccwar nnes \add innuffaren\add* i imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen.  
\v 8 Ayrad izehhar, man wen war itteggʷden? Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa issiweř, man wen war ittnebba?’”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Jjem ad ittwaseř aya di řeqṣur di Acdud u di řeqṣur n temmurt n Miṣra, ini: ‘Munem x idurar n Samarya u xzarem anehweř ameqqran di řwesṭ nnes u inni dayes ittwaḥṣaren!’  
\v 10 Nitni war ssinen mammec ɣa ggen min iseggden, iqqar SIDI, nitni inni iyarrwen lɛunf d tkeccaḍt di řeqṣur nsen.’  
\v 11 S uya, ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: ‘Ijj n řeɛdu! Netta ittenneḍ i temmurt \add marra\add*! Ad issehwa jjehd nnem zzayem u řeqṣur nnem ad ttwakeccḍen.’ \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Ica. 28:1-3\x*  
\v 12 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Am ifekk ijj n umeksaw tnayen n iḍaren niɣ ijj n yixef n umezzuɣ zeg uqemmum n wayrad, ammu i ɣa ttwassnejmen ayt n Israil, inni \add i din\add* ittɣiman di Samarya x tma n qama u x yict n tzerbiyyet zi Dimacq ggin tt x yict n řemṭarbet.’”   
\m
\v 13 “Sřem u cehdem di taddart n Yaɛqub, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat.  
\v 14 Minzi deg wass nni di ɣa xeřfeɣ ixeṭṭan n Israil, ad ssiwḍeɣ \add ɛawed\add* axeǧeṣ x iɛalṭaren n Bayt-Il, \add maɣar\add* ad ttwaqeḍɛen waccawen n uɛalṭar, ad wḍan ɣar temmurt.  
\v 15 Necc ad hedmeɣ tazeddiɣt n tgarst d tzeddiɣt n unebdu u tudrin n řɛaj ad ttwaqḍant, u aṭṭas n tudrin ad ttwaredǧent!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \f ◼ \fr 3:15 \ft \+fk řɛaj\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘accawen n lfil’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Israil war tᵉttub ca  
\m
\v 1 “Sřent, awař-a, \add a\add* tifunasin n Bacan nni \add iǧan\add* x wedrar n Samarya, tinni iḥeṣṣaren imuqřiřen, tinni iɛeffsen x imezřaḍ, tinni iqqaren i aytbab nsen: ‘Awyem-dd \add ca\add* \add ařami\add* i ɣa nessu!’  
\v 2 Sidi inu, SIDI, ijjuǧ s tqeddast nnes, aqa ad xakent dd-kken wussan, ad kennint kksen s iɣantcuten u min zzaykent iqqimen s tṣennarin n iseřman.  
\v 3 Kennint ad teffɣent zi tizzeyyin n řeḥyuḍ, kuř ict n temɣart nican ɣar zzat. Kennint ad ttwassekkent ɣar Harmun, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.   
\m
\v 4 \add Iwa,\add* asem-dd ɣar Bayt-Il u ɛeddam, \add asem-dd ɣar\add* Jiljal u arnim deg iɛeddiyen nwem. \add Iwa,\add* awyem-dd tiɣarṣa nwem kuř ṣṣbeḥ d řeɛcur nwem ict n twařa di třata n wussan! \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Ḥuc. 12:12\x*  
\v 5 \add Iwa,\add* sbexxar ict n tewhibt n uqadi s \add weɣrum ak-d\add* wentun u řaɣam, \add maḥend ad qeddmen\add* tiwhibin s řxaḍar, barrḥem zzayes, maɣar ammu i d awem itteɛjib, \add a\add* ayt n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 4:5 \xt Lawi 2:1, 15; 7:13\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Ɛawed Necc jjiɣ awem tazdugi n teɣmas di marra tineddam nwem u tuqřič n weɣrum di marra imucan nwem \add mani tzeddɣem\add*. \bd \+bdit Qaɛ amenni maca\+bdit* kenniw war dd-tedwiřem ɣari\bd*, iqqar SIDI.   
\m
\v 7 Necc ssbeddeɣ xawem anẓar umi din \add ɛad\add* třata n iyuren ař tmeyra u Necc ggiɣ ad iwwet wenẓar x ict n tendint, \add maca\add* di tendint nneɣni war ggiɣ ad iwwet wenẓar. Ijj n yeyyar immewc as wenẓar u iyyar nneɣni i x war iwti wenẓar, inẓeɣ.  
\v 8 Tnayen, třata n tneddam uyurent ttenhezzant ɣar ict n tendint nneɣni, maḥend ad swent aman, \add maca\add* nitenti war jjiwnent ca. \bd \+bdit Qaɛ amenni maca\+bdit* kenniw war dd-tedwiřem ɣari\bd*, iqqar SIDI.   
\m
\v 9 Necc wtiɣ kenniw s \add imendi\add* ittwasscemḍen \add zeg usemmiḍ\add*, s jjriḥect n wefsu. Aṭṭas n iḥwicen nwem d imarjaɛen nwem n uḍiř d wurtan nwem d tzitunin nwem aqa icca i-ten bu-weqḍeɛ. \bd \+bdit Qaɛ amenni maca\+bdit* kenniw war dd-tedwiřem ɣari\bd*, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Aɛwd. 28:22; Yuw. 1:4\x*   
\m
\v 10 Necc ssekkeɣ-dd jar awem ṭṭaɛun, am mammec ggiɣ di Miṣra. Necc nɣiɣ iḥudriyen nwem s ssif, iysan nwem nedheɣ ten d takeccaḍṭ u arriɣ arriḥet n řɛeskarat nwem ad tgeɛɛed ař wenzaren nwem. \bd \+bdit Qaɛ amenni maca\+bdit* kenniw war dd-tedwiřem ɣari\bd*, iqqar SIDI.   
\m
\v 11 Necc ssenqeřbeɣ kenniw am mammec tuɣa issneqřab AREBBI Sadum d Ɛamurra. Tuɣa kenniw am yijj n ukeccuḍ di tmessi nni dd-ittwaqeřɛen zeg \add uḥaduq n\add* tmessi. \bd \+bdit Qaɛ amenni maca\+bdit* kenniw war dd-tedwiřem ɣari\bd*, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt 19:24\x*   
\m
\v 12 S uya Necc ad ac ggeɣ aya, \add a\add* Israil! Minzi Necc ad ac ggeɣ man aya, ḥezzem \add ixef nnec\add*, \add a\add* Israil, maḥend ad temmeřqid ak-d AREBBI nnec.  
\v 13 Maɣar xzar, d Netta i ikewwnen idurar u ittejja-dd asemmiḍ u isscan min di ittxarreṣ, d wenni ittarran tuffut n řḥař d taǧest u iggur tiwa i řegɛudi n temmurt, aqa: SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Nḥm. 1:3\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Acetci n SIDI x Israil  
\m
\v 1 “Sřem awař-a i xawem ssekkareɣ, ijj n yezři n ugejdur, \add a\add* taddart n Israil.   
\b  
\m
\v 2 \qt “Aqa tewḍa teɛzarect Israil,\qt*  
\m \qt war tᵉttekkar ɛad.\qt*  
\m \qt Nettat temmenḍar ɣar temmurt nnes,\qt*  
\m \qt war din uřa d ijj i tt ɣa issbedden.”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 3 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI: Tandint nni i ɣa iffɣen s wařef \add n yeryazen\add*, ad as tceṭṭ mya, u tenni i ɣa iffɣen s mya, ad as tceṭṭ ɛecra i taddart n Israil.  
\v 4 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI ɣar taddart n Israil: Arzum xafi, xenni ad teddarem!”  
\v 5 War tarezzfem Bayt-Il, war dd-tᵉttisem ɣar Jiljal u war ɛeddum x Bi’r-Sebɛa, minzi s tidett Jiljal ad ittwandeh ɣar lmenfa u Bayt-Il ad tᵉttwabeṭṭeř. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Ɛam. 4:4\x*  
\v 6 Arzum x SIDI, xenni ad teddarem, ḥima Netta war ittidif ɣar taddart n Yusuf am yict n tmessi ittetten u war din ittiři uřa d ijj maḥend ad \add tt\add* issexsi di ṭṭweɛ n Bayt-Il.”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “\add Axeyyeb i\add* yinni ittarran řḥeqq ɣar cciḥ u inni isshekkʷan tasegda ɣar temmurt.  
\v 8 Netta d wenni iggin Ipliyaden d Uriyun d wenni ittarran tiři n řmewt d tuffut n řḥař, d wenni \add ittarran\add* ass d ǧiřet, wenni ittřaɣan i waman n řebḥar u ifarreɣ i-ten tiwa i wudem n temmurt, aqa SIDI d Isem nnes!, \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Ayub 9:9; 38:31; Ɛam. 9:6\x*  
\v 9 aqa Netta igga ad dd-yas wareddeǧ \add am\add* wassam x wenni ijehden u \add aqa yarra\add* areddeǧ ad dd-yas x lqelɛa.  
\v 10 \add Maca\add* nitni carrhen wenni iddafaɛen x řḥeqq di tewwart \add n tendint\add* u nitni ttɛiffan wenni issawařen nican.  
\v 11 S uya, minzi kenniw tɛeffsem x umuqřiř u tᵉttkessem zzayes řeɛcur n imendi: \add waxxa\add* tebnam tudrin nwem s weẓru yuydan, war daysent tzeddɣem, \add waxxa\add* teẓẓum tizayarin cnant deg imarjaɛen, war zzaysent tsessem binu. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Ṣaf. 1:13\x*  
\v 12 Maɣar Necc ssneɣ aṭṭas n iɛeddiyen nwem u aqa ddnub nwem sseggʷaden: nitni ḥeṣṣaren amsegged, ttᵉṭṭfen tmenyat n řɣecc u ɛarrnen imezřaḍ ɣar barra di tewwart \add n tendint\add*.  
\v 13 S uya ad isseɣd umiɣis di řweqt nni, maɣar ad tiři d ict n řweqt d taɛeffant.”   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Arzum min iṣebḥen, war iǧi min iɛeffnen, xenni ad kidwem yiři SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, am mammec \add t\add* teqqarem kenniw.  
\v 15 Carhem min iɛeffnen, texsem min iṣebḥen u smetnem řḥeqq di tewwart \add n tendint\add*. Ad taɣ ad iḥinn SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat x min iqqimen n Yusuf.” \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt Izhd. 34:15; 97:10; Rum. 12:9\x*  
\v 16 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, Sidi inu: Di marra azzayen ad tiři tɣuyyit n wecḍan u di marra zznaqi ad inin: ‘Ayyaw! Ayyaw!’, u nitni ad řaɣan x ufeǧaḥ, maḥend ad icḍen, u x yinni issnen izřan n wecḍan maḥend ad sɣuyen s wecḍan.  
\v 17 Di marra imarjaɛen n uḍiř \add ad din tiři\add* tɣuyyit n wecḍan, maɣar Necc ad cuqeɣ di řwest nnec, iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 18 “Ayyaw i yinni ittmeẓren deg wass n SIDI! Min ɣarwem i ɣa yiři wass n SIDI? \add Ad yiři\add* d taǧest, war ittiři d tafawt. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Irm. 30:7; Yuw. 2:2; Ṣaf. 1:15\x*  
\v 19 \add Ad yiři\add* am ca n ijj i yarewřen zeg wayrad, xenni yusa-dd ɣares ddub, niɣ am ca n ijj i yudfen ɣar taddart, iɛemmed s ufus nnes x řḥiḍ, xenni izɛef i-t ijj n ufiɣar.  
\v 20 \add Ma\add* war ittiři ass n SIDI d taǧest u war ittiři d tfawt? D ṭṭřam u war \add teǧi\add* uřa d ict n jjurret n tfawt!”   
\b  
\m
\v 21 “Necc carrheɣ, ɛiffeɣ uraren nwem u war ttexseɣ ad cemmeɣ imuniten nwem ifarzen. \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Ica. 1:11; Irm. 6:20\x*  
\v 22 Maɣar waxxa kenniw tiwyem ayi-d tiɣarṣa nwem n wecmaḍ d tewhibin nwem \add n řɣiǧet\add*, Necc war xasent areṭṭiɣ ca u Necc war xezzareɣ \add walu\add* ɣar tewhibt n řehna n řmař iṣeḥḥen.  
\v 23 Siggʷej xafi ddriz n izřan nnec, war xseɣ ad sřeɣ řḥess n lharpat nnec.  
\v 24 Ejj řḥukm ad yazzeř am waman \add ittazzřen\add* u tasegda am yijj n iɣzar ittazzřen řebda.”   
\b  
\m
\v 25 “Ma tiwyem ayi-dd tiɣarṣa d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* di řexřa arebɛin n iseggʷusa, \add a\add* taddart n Israil? \x ◘ \xo 5:25 \xt Řex. 7:42\x*  
\v 26 Kenniw tarbum iqiḍan n ujeǧid nwem d uḍar \add i xef tuɣa\add* ttbeddan řexyařat nwem \add i\add* yetri n irebbiten nwem, inni teggim i yixef nwem.  
\v 27 Necc ad kenniw nedheɣ ɣar lmenfa, aɣirin i Dimacq, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, aqa d wa d Isem nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\m
\v 1 “Uct x yinni war di yeǧi bu wemnus di Ṣihyun u x yinni umi ittɣiř aqa aten di řaman x wedrar n Samarya, imcennɛen n wenni d amezwaru jar řegnus, i ɣares dd-tᵉttas \add marra\add* taddart n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt Uf. 19:5; Irm. 2:3\x*   
\m
\v 2 Ɛdum ɣar Kalna u txezzarem \add mammec teǧa\add*! Uyurem ssenni ɣar Ḥamat u hwam-dd ɣar Jat n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Ma nitni ḥsen zi tgeldawin-a niɣ tammurt nsen d tameqqrant x temmurt nwem? \f ◼ \fr 6:2 \ft \+fk tigeldawin-a\ft  - ixs ad yini Israil d Yahuda.\f*   
\m
\v 3 \add Kenniw\add*, inni issbeɛɛden ass aɛeffan ɣar zzat nwem, \add maca\add* tessqarrabem řkuřsi n lɛunf,\x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Ḥiz. 12:27; Ɛam. 5:18\x*  
\v 4 \add kenniw\add*, inni i \add din\add* ittezzřen x qamat n řɛaj uca ttesṭiřen x řemṭarbat nwem u ttᵉtten izmaren n wuǧi uřa d iɛejmiyyen zi řwesṭ n řkuri, \f ◼ \fr 6:4 \ft \+fk iɛejmiyyen\ft  - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  
\v 5 inni i \add din\add* iɣennjen amenni waha ɣar ǧɣa n lharpa, am dd-ssuffɣen \add ɛřam kuř n\add* izřan s dduzan n lmusiqa, am mammec \add t igga\add* Dawud, \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Ica. 5:12\x*  
\v 6 inni isessen binu zi ṭṭawyat n urucci, inni idehhnen ixef nsen s řemxeyyar n zzect u war ttarran taynit i treẓẓit n Yusuf. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Ica. 5:11, 12\x*  
\v 7 S uya ad uyuren nitni řexxu ɣar lmenfa ɣar uzeǧif n imenfiyyen. Aqa ittwaqḍa ddriz n uɣuyyi n yinni i \add din\add* ittɣiman \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Ica. 5:13\x*   
\m
\v 8 Sidi inu, SIDI ijjuǧ s yixef nnes, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat: Necc ɛiffeɣ nnfaxet n Yaɛqub u carrheɣ řeqṣur nnes. S uyenni ad sellmeɣ tandint d marra min dayes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Ad imsar řami qqimen ɛecra n iryazen di taddart d ict, \add aqa\add* ad mmten nitni.  
\v 10 \add Mařa\add* ɛemmis, wenni xas maḥend ad t isscemḍ, ad t iksi ḥima ad issuffeɣ řxecbet zi taddart, uca \add xenni\add* ad yini i wenni \add ɛad\add* ɣar daxeř di taddart: ‘Ma aqa din ɣarek ɛad ktar?’, uca ad yini wenneɣni: ‘Uřa d ijj!’, \add xenni\add* ad yini netta: ‘Sqar, minzi ittxeṣṣa war nettidar Isem n SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Maɣar xzar, SIDI ittamar, uca Netta ad iwwet taddart tameqqrant ař ɣa tedweř d řxarbet u taddart tameẓyant \add ad tedweř\add* d iceǧiqen.  
\v 12 Ma ad tazzřen iysan x řejruf? Ma ad t carzen s ifunasen? Kenniw maca tarrim řḥeqq d arrhaj u řɣiǧet n tsegda tarrim tt d cciḥ. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt Ɛam. 5:7\x*  
\v 13 \add Kenniw\add* inni ifarrḥen zi min war iǧin, inni iqqaren: ‘Ma war neṭṭif accawen s jjehd nneɣ?’  
\v 14 Maɣar xzar, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, Necc ad dd-ssekkareɣ ijj n řgens ḍidd nwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat. Nitni ad kenniw ḥṣaren zi manis dd-iwḍen \add iwdan\add* ɣar Ḥamat ař taɣzart n Řewḍa.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Tameẓriwt tamezwarut: iburexsen  
\m
\v 1 “Man aya isscen ayi \add tt\add* Sidi inu, SIDI! Xzar, Netta igga iburexsen umi tuɣa arbiɛ aneggar ibedda ad issuffeɣ. Xzar, tuɣa-t d arbiɛ aneggar awarni ma ḥetcen \add arbiɛ\add* i ujeǧid.  
\v 2 Imsar, umi kemmřen nitni zi macca n uɣemmuy aziza n temmurt, necc nniɣ: ‘\add A\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, sameḥ maca! Mammec i ɣa yegg Yaɛqub ad iqqim ad ibedd, aqa netta d ameẓyan!’  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* indem SIDI x man aya. ‘War ittiři!’, inna SIDI.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss tnayen: timessi ihellken  
\m
\v 4 “Man aya isscen ayi \add tt\add* Sidi inu, SIDI. Xzar, Sidi inu, SIDI, iřaɣa-dd maḥend ad din yiři lɛiqab s tmessi uca \add timessi\add* tecca \add aman\add* imeqqranen ihewřen ařami ad tecc \add uřa d\add* tasɣart \add n řwart\add*. \f ◼ \fr 7:4 \ft \+fk řwart\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘tammurt n Israil’ i iwca SIDI i ayt n Israil.\f*  
\v 5 Necc nniɣ: ‘\add A\add* Sidi inu, SIDI, sbedd maca! Mammec i ɣa yegg Yaɛqub ad iqqim ad ibedd, aqa netta d ameẓyan!’  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* indem SIDI x man aya. ‘War ittiři!’, inna Sidi inu, SIDI!”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss třata: plumu n řḥiḍ  
\m
\v 7 “Man aya isscen ayi \add tt\add* Netta: Xzar, Sidi inu ibedd x yijj n řḥiḍ i ittwagg s plumu u yijj n plumu tuɣa deg ufus nnes.  
\v 8 Inna ayi SIDI: ‘Min tᵉttwarid cek, Ɛamus?’ Necc nniɣ: ‘Ijj n plumu!’ \add Řexdenni\add* inna Sidi: ‘Xzar, Necc ad arreɣ plumu inu di řwesṭ n řgens n Israil. Necc war xas ɛedduɣ ɛad!  
\v 9 Řegɛudi n Isḥaq ad ttwareddǧent u tizawiyyin iqeddsen n Israil ad dewřent d řxarbet u Necc ad kkareɣ x taddart n Yarubɛam s ssif.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ajeǧid Amaṣya ixs ad yaẓẓeř x Ɛamus zi temmurt  
\m
\v 10 \add Řexdenni\add* issekk Amaṣya, akehhan di Bayt-Il, \add ijjen\add* ɣar Yarubɛam, ajeǧid n Israil, inna: “Ɛamus igga ijj n řɛahd ḍidd i cek di řwesṭ n taddart n Israil. Tammurt war tzemmar ad teksi awařen nnes.  
\v 11 Maɣar ammu i iqqar Ɛamus: ‘Yarubɛam ad ittwaneɣ s ssif u Israil ad ittwandeh ɣar lmenfa, ad t ssiggʷejen x wudem n temmurt nnes.’”  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna Amaṣya i Ɛamus: “\add A\add* cek, amwařaw, ruḥ, arweř ɣar temmurt n Yahuda! Ecc dinni aɣrum u nabb dinni!  
\v 13 Di Bayt-Il \add maca\add* war tzemmared ad tnebbid ɛad, minzi nettat d zzawect iqeddsen n ujeǧid u nettat d taddart n tageldit.”   
\m
\v 14 Yarra-dd Ɛamus, inna i Amaṣya: “Necc war ǧiɣ d anabi u necc war ǧiɣ d mmis n unabi, maca necc tuɣa ayi d bu-řebhayem uřa d ijj n weryaz nni iřeqqḍen tazart taburect.  
\v 15 SIDI ikkes ayi zi ḍeffar n wuǧi u SIDI inna ayi: ‘Uyur, nabb i řgens inu Israil!’  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, seř i wawař n SIDI, cek d wenni iqqaren: ‘War iɛeddeř ad tnebbid ḍidd i Israil u ad tessudmed \add awař n SIDI\add* x taddart n Isḥaq!’ \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Ḥiz. 21:7\x*  
\v 17 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: Tamɣart nnec ad tessefsed ixef nnes s uɣiř di tendint u iḥenjiren nnec d yessic nnec ad wḍan s ssif u tammurt nnec ad tt bḍan s ufiřu n řeɛbar u cek ad temmted deg ict n temmurt texmej u s tidett Israil ad tᵉttwaṭṭef di lmenfa barra i temmurt nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss arebɛa: tasuǧet s řɣiǧet  
\m
\v 1 “Man aya isscen ayi \add tt\add* Sidi inu, SIDI: Xzar, ict n tsuǧet dayes tini n unebdu!  
\v 2 Netta inna: ‘Min tᵉttwařid cek a Ɛamus?’ Necc nniɣ: ‘Ict n tsuǧet dayes tini n unebdu!’ \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: ‘Aqa yusa-dd qeṭṭu x řgens inu Israil. Necc war xas ɛedduɣ ɛad!  
\v 3 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad dewřen izřan n řeqṣar d imeṭṭawen, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI. Ad iřint aṭṭas n řxecbat di kuř amcan, tinni inḍar Netta. Seɣd!’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iɛřamen imeqqranen n SIDI  
\m
\v 4 “Sřem aya, kenniw inni iṣarrḍen amezřuḍ u teqḍam x řmusakin n temmurt,  
\v 5 am teqqarem: ‘Meřmi ɣa iɛdu uyur n jdid ařami \add nzemmar\add* ad nezzenz řḥebb \add n yirden\add*. U \add meřmi ɣa iɛdu wass n\add* ssebt ařami \add nzemmar\add* ad narzem tisrafin \add n yirden\add*, ḥima ad nessemẓi \add řeɛbar n\add* ifa u ad nessemɣar ciqlu u ad necmet s řmizanat n řɣecc, \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Ḥuc. 12:8\x*  
\v 6 ařami nzemmar ad nseɣ imuqřiřen s \add tenɛacin n\add* nnuqart uřa d amezřuḍ i tyuya n sandaliyat!’, u \add am teqqarem\add*: ‘Ad nezzenz icarfa deg wemcan n imendi!’”\x ◘ \xo 8:6 \xt Ɛam. 2:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “SIDI ijjuǧ ɣar nnfaxet n Yaɛqub: ‘Ɛemmarṣ ad ttuɣ timegga nsen!  
\v 8 Ma war ttenhezzi temmurt s man aya u ma war ttiřin marra imezdaɣ nnes ceḍnen? Ma war tᵉttgeɛɛid \add temmurt\add* tmun am yeɣzar, ad taři u ad dd-tehwa am yeɣzar n Miṣra?”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad imsar, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, ad arreɣ tfuct ad teɣři deg wezyen n wass u ad ssbarecneɣ tammurt ɣar ṭḥa n wass.  
\v 10 Necc ad arreɣ fictat nwem d acḍan d marra izřan nwem d izřan n wecḍan u Necc ad ggeɣ ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* x marra tbeysa u x kuř azeǧif ad ggeɣ tuqeccart. Ad awyeɣ acḍan \add x temmurt\add* am \add wecḍan\add* x uyenni n mmis, u \add a\add*qeṭṭu nnes ad t ggeɣ am yijj n wass d amarzag.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa Necc ad ssekkeɣ řaẓ x temmurt, war iǧi řaẓ n weɣrum, war iǧi fad n waman, maca \add ijj n ufadi\add* maḥend ad sřen i wawařen n SIDI.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ad ttelɛen zi řebḥar ɣar řebḥar u zi ccamal ɣar ccarq, ad uyuren zi ssa ɣar da maḥend ad arzun x wawař n SIDI, \add maca\add* war t ttifen.  
\v 13 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ɣacant teɛzariyyin nni icnan qaɛ uřa d iḥudriyyen s ufadi,  
\v 14 inni ittjjaǧan ɣar umarwas n Samarya, qqaren: ‘S tidett am iddar arebbi nnec, \add a\add* Dan, u am iddar webrid ɣar Bi’r-Sebɛa!’, ad wḍan, war ttekkaren ɛad!” \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Ɛam. 5:5\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Tameẓriwt wiss xemsa: řḥukm aneggaru  
\m
\v 1 “Necc ẓriɣ Sidi inu ibedd ɣar uɛalṭar, inna: ‘Wwet x uzeǧif \add n upilar\add*, \add ařami\add* i ɣa arjijent tnebdatin u arẓ i-tent d iwetwiten x uzeǧif nsen marra. Min zzaysen iqqimen, ad t nɣeɣ s ssif. War zzaysen ittrikkʷiř uřa d ijj n umarwař u uřa d ijj wenni inejjmen, ad ittwafekk.  
\v 2 Waxxa nitni ɣzin ařami \add iwḍen ɣar\add* tmessi n řaxart, afus inu ad ten ssenni yawi, u waxxa nitni geɛɛaden ɣar ujenna, Necc ad ten dd ssenni ssehwiɣ, \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Izhd. 139:8-10\x*  
\v 3 waxxa nitni ssnuffaren ixef nsen x tqiccat n \add wedrar n\add* Karmil, Necc ad arzuɣ u ad ten dd-awyeɣ ssenni. Waxxa nitni ssnuffaren ixef nsen zzat i tiṭṭawin inu x tisi n řebḥar, xenni Necc ad weṣṣiɣ afiɣar maḥend ad ten izɛef,  
\v 4 u waxxa nitni uyuren di tmeḥbast zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nsen, Necc ad weṣṣiɣ dinni ssif maḥend ad ten ineɣ. Necc ad xasen nḍareɣ tiṭṭ inu i řɣar, war iǧi i řxar. \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Irm. 44:11\x*  
\v 5 Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, Netta d wenni ittḥadan tammurt, \add ařami\add* tenhezz u marra imezdaɣ nnes ceḍnen. Tᵉttgeɛɛed tmun am yeɣzar n Nil uca tᵉttaři thekkwi am yeɣzar n Miṣra.  
\v 6 Netta d wenni ibennan ixxamen nnes sennej deg ujenna u ittegg řqubbet nnes x temmurt, Netta d wenni ittřaɣan i waman n řebḥar uca ittfarreɣ i-ten x wudem n temmurt, SIDI d Isem nnes.\x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Izhd. 104:3, 13; Ɛam. 5:8\x*  
\v 7 Ma kenniw war teǧim inu am ayt n Kuc, \add a\add* ayt n Israil?, iqqar SIDI. Ma Necc war dd-ssuffɣeɣ Israil zi Miṣra u Ifilisṭiniyyen zi Kaftur u Aram zi Qir?  
\v 8 Xzarem, tiṭṭawin n Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa atent ḍidd i tgeldit tamednubt. Necc ad tt teḥḥiɣ zeg wudem n temmurt. Necc maca war tteḥḥiɣ marra taddart n Yaɛqub, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 9 Maɣar xzarem, Necc ad umureɣ u ad zzeřzeɣ taddart n Israil jar marra řegnus, am mammec zzeřzen zzariɛet deg ijj n bu-siyyar u war tweṭṭi uřa d ict n tḥebbuct ɣar temmurt.  
\v 10 Marra imednab n řgens inu ad ttwanɣen s ssif, inni iqqaren: ‘Řɣar war d aneɣ iřeqqef ca u war ɣarneɣ dd-ittqarrib ca zi marra iɣezdisen!’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “\bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ ɛawed taxzant iweṭṭan n Dawud i iwḍan u Necc ad qqneɣ tizza nnes u min zzayes ittwahedmen, ad t arreɣ ɣar wemcan nnes u Necc ad t bniɣ \add ɛawed\add* am deg wussan n wecḥař uya, \x ◘ \xo 9:11 \xt Řex. 15:16\x*  
\v 12 maḥend nitni ad warten min iqqimen zi Idum d marra řegnus i x ittwabarreḥ s Yisem inu, iqqar SIDI wenni itteggen marra aya.  
\v 13 Xzarem, ad dd-asen wussan, iqqar SIDI, aqa wenni icarrzen ad xas dd-iḥart wenni imejjaren, u wenni iřebbzen aḍiř s iḍaren \add ad xas dd-iḥart\add* wenni isswiẓẓḍen \add afus ak-d\add* zzariɛet, u idurar ad ttucruren s binu ẓemmen t jdid, u marra tiwririn ad ssefyent. \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Yuw. 4:18\x*  
\v 14 Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast x řgens inu Israil u nitni ad bnan ɛawed tineddam i tuɣa ittwahedmen u ad daysent zeddɣen u nitni ad ggen imarjaɛen n uḍiř ad daysen ẓẓun tizayarin u ad zzaysent swen binu, ad ggen iḥwicen ad ccen řɣiǧet nnes.  
\v 15 Necc ad ten ẓẓuɣ di temmurt nsen u ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad ttwaqeřɛen zi temmurt nsen nni i d asen wciɣ, iqqar SIDI, AREBBI nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Irm. 32:41\x*   